{"id":1043,"date":"2019-12-28T15:41:54","date_gmt":"2019-12-28T15:41:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/golangbyexamples.com\/?p=1043"},"modified":"2019-12-28T16:38:57","modified_gmt":"2019-12-28T16:38:57","slug":"go-selection-sort","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/golangbyexamples.com\/go-selection-sort\/","title":{"rendered":"Selection Sort in Go(Golang)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_17 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"><\/i><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-1\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/golangbyexamples.com\/go-selection-sort\/#Introduction\" title=\"Introduction\">Introduction<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-1\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/golangbyexamples.com\/go-selection-sort\/#Time_Complexity\" title=\"Time Complexity\">Time Complexity<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-1\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/golangbyexamples.com\/go-selection-sort\/#Space_Complexity\" title=\"Space Complexity\">Space Complexity<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-1\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/golangbyexamples.com\/go-selection-sort\/#Implementation\" title=\"Implementation:\">Implementation:<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Introduction\"><\/span><strong>Introduction<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">In selection sort, we maintain two parts<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"has-medium-font-size wp-block-list\"><li>Sorted Part<\/li><li>Unsorted Part <\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-medium-font-size wp-block-list\"><li>In each iteration, the max or min element (depending upon order is asc or desc) is picked from the unsorted part and then is put at the end of the sorted part.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-medium-font-size wp-block-list\"><li>Hence the length of the sorted part in each iteration increases by 1. In the end, the entire array is sorted.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Time_Complexity\"><\/span><strong>Time Complexity<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-medium-font-size wp-block-list\"><li>O(n*n)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Space_Complexity\"><\/span><strong>Space Complexity<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-medium-font-size wp-block-list\"><li>Space Complexity of selection sort is O(1)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Implementation\"><\/span><strong>Implementation:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-prismatic-blocks\"><code class=\"language-go\">package main\n\nimport \"fmt\"\n\nfunc main() {\n    sample := []int{3, 4, 5, 2, 1}\n    selectionSort(sample)\n    sample = []int{3, 4, 5, 2, 1, 7, 8, -1, -3}\n    selectionSort(sample)\n}\n\nfunc selectionSort(arr []int) {\n    len := len(arr)\n    for i := 0; i < len-1; i++ {\n        minIndex := i\n        for j := i + 1; j < len; j++ {\n            if arr[j] < arr[minIndex] {\n                arr[j], arr[minIndex] = arr[minIndex], arr[j]\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    fmt.Println(\"\\nAfter SelectionSort\")\n    for _, val := range arr {\n        fmt.Println(val)\n    }\n}<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Output:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-prismatic-blocks\"><code class=\"language-go\">After SelectionSort\n1\n2\n3\n4\n5\n\nAfter SelectionSort\n-3\n-1\n1\n2\n3\n4\n5\n7\n8<\/code><\/pre>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Table of Contents IntroductionTime ComplexitySpace ComplexityImplementation: Introduction In selection sort, we maintain two parts Sorted Part Unsorted Part In each iteration, the max or min element (depending upon order is asc or&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"spay_email":"","footnotes":"","jetpack_publicize_message":"","jetpack_is_tweetstorm":false},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1043","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-tech"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v22.7 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Selection Sort in Go(Golang) - Welcome To Golang By Example<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/golangbyexamples.com\/go-selection-sort\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Selection Sort in Go(Golang) - Welcome To Golang By Example\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Table of Contents IntroductionTime ComplexitySpace ComplexityImplementation: Introduction In selection sort, we maintain two parts Sorted Part Unsorted Part In each iteration, the max or min element (depending upon order is asc or...\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/golangbyexamples.com\/go-selection-sort\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Welcome To Golang 